    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Ten of thirteen credibility factors have been assessed and all meet or exceed required levels for MRL 3. Three factors (Test samples, Use error, Equivalency of input parameters) are carried as not-assessed on the basis that their evaluation is considered beyond the current project scope. The assessed factors collectively provide sufficient evidence to support the intended use decision. The not-assessed factors are acknowledged but the team judges the overall credibility adequate for the CPB hemolysis identification decision.",
